metadata.name: Blood color
metadata.description:
I dreamed of this image.  
I can't tell if I was asleep or awake, but I longed to feel the true color my eyes saw when they closed.  
I needed to understand the meaning of all that blood circulating in my veins.  
I needed to represent this in an image while I'm feeling alive, will I be seeing life in full when I find the meaning of all this color when I close my eyelids.  
I hope to find all the sense I lack before they finish their work, before all this color, this color of blood, runs out.

Blood 2/2/2022.

- The winner of the auction will received the piece in acrylic frame and manuscript on tissue paper.
